name: Aveeno Baby Daily Care Gift Set with Natural Oat Extract & Oatmeal, Contains Daily Moisturizing Body Lotion & Gentle 2-in-1 Baby Bath Wash & Shampoo, Hypoallergenic & Paraben-Free, 2 Items
descriptions:
Aveeno Baby Daily Care Gift Set containing one 12-fluid ounce bottle of Aveeno 2-in-1 Baby Bath Wash & Shampoo and one 12-fluid ounce bottle of Aveeno Baby Moisturizing .Body Lotion for daily nourishment of your babies' sensitive skin and hair.
Convenient set of baby bath & skincare products are specially designed for baby's delicate skin and hair to leave it feeling soft, smooth and healthy looking.
Baby body wash & shampoo contains natural oat extract. The formula is tear-free, hypoallergenic, pH-balanced & free of soap, sulfates, parabens, phthalates & phenoxyethanol. It can be used on skin & hair and rinses clean with a light, fresh fragrance.
Fragrance-free lotion contains natural oatmeal & dimethicone to soothe baby's delicate skin. The non-greasy formula absorbs quickly and moisturizes for a full 24 hours. It is hypoallergenic & is free of parabens, phthalates, steroids & phenoxyethanol.
From Aveeno, a pediatrician and dermatologist recommended brand, both of these Aveeno baby skincare products use high quality, natural oats, and carefully harvest their moisturizing and soothing properties.

name: LEGO DUPLO Construction Truck & Tracked Excavator 10931 Toddler Building Toy for Kids Aged 2 and up (20 Pieces)
descriptions:
Toddlers improve their fine motor skills as they drive the train then load, unload, stack and sort the number bricks. As children explore play possibilities, they also discover colors and numbers.
With its cute characters and colorful, easy-to-handle bricks, the Number Train is ideal for toddlers aged 18 months and up  and for parents keen to share their preschoolers developmental milestones.
The playset measures over 3.5 in. (10 cm) high and 18.5 in. (47 cm) long and combines easily with other LEGO DUPLO sets to inspire even more imaginative play possibilities.
